{"tid":584273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[恨鐵不成鋼]香港人唔好咁鵪鶉得唔得？","createTime":"2018-03-07T16:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T02:46:36.000Z","uid":87511,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b8047e79072244e52662850603b79387c75285f6","tid":584273,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T16:56:01.000Z","msg":"繁忙時間，關愛座有位，成棚人塞鳩住個車廂，就係冇人敢坐，怕畀人影上網<br />\n<br />\n女仔畀人偷拍／非禮唔敢報警，又係怕麻煩怕見報（明明新聞都只係會用&quot;X / Y&quot;稱呼女事主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n）；就算有好心人幫手捉色狼，都會想放過隻色狼一馬<br />\n<br />\n等巴士等地鐵畀廢中廢老打尖，唔敢出聲，遲上一班車都好過同人嘈；就算有義士出嚟屌，都唔會幫口<br />\n<br />\n同事合理爭取加薪，唔支持，話鳩知佢死，lam份雞水咁多嘅人工就心足<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔鍾意香港，但係有時都好懷疑自己呢一代人係咪已經變哂喪屍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解後生仔女都係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb8891de0ee0351e9187c1cef3856f8efab0fd5","tid":584273,"uid":87732,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T16:58:50.000Z","msg":"網絡影響力太大 俾人擺上網真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a72e271529f47ca78a193d88ada37c748fab9aa","tid":584273,"uid":87511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9cb8891de0ee0351e9187c1cef3856f8efab0fd5","tid":584273,"uid":87732,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T16:58:50.000Z","msg":"網絡影響力太大 俾人擺上網真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T17:10:04.000Z","msg":"就係你呢種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你入嚟完美示範<br />\n<br />\n老老實實，仲有冇人記得幾年前嗰啲坐關愛座畀人放上網嘅後生仔？<br />\n就算放上網，輿論又係咪一面倒屌鳩啲後生仔？<br />\n<br />\n自己唔buy呢套但係都帶頭驚，就冇人改變到呢股歪風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8218dd8e1e23653a270de20163c9c74d11b824eb","tid":584273,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T17:12:14.000Z","msg":"香港人不嬲弱勢<br />\n強勢係回歸前既鬼佬"},{"pid":"05001ecc4ff2dcd60a7b2bf76bb533dc9d7afc8b","tid":584273,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T18:34:51.000Z","msg":"你出post 既連登正正就係一個公審人既地方"},{"pid":"d17c317fe77458aef0da77eeaf96793f93fb6cd8","tid":584273,"uid":9863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T01:35:54.000Z","msg":"從來關愛座想坐就照坐 唔覺得有咩問題<br />\n反正見到有需要嘅人  係唔係關愛座都照讓"},{"pid":"9ee31686c33219d4596898bb40151ddb19958a3b","tid":584273,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T02:46:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}